title: Marvels Jessica Jones Trailer Is Finally Here and Krysten Ritter Is Going to Kick Your Ass
text:
Marvel's Jessica Jones Trailer Is Finally Here and Krysten Ritter Is Going to Kick Your Ass 
E online Friday 23rd October, 2015 
and the Marvel movies you love so much. Ritter is Jessica Jones, a superhero who gives up the life following tragedy and starts her own private investigation operation. However, she didn't give up the superpowers, including super strength and the ability to jump super high, which you can see in the trailer below....
